## 📡 API Endpoints

### Base URL: `http://localhost:3002/api/cart`

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|--------|----------|-------------|------|
| POST | `/` | Add item to cart | None |
| GET | `/?guestToken={token}` | Get cart contents | None |
| PUT | `/:id` | Update cart item quantity | None |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Remove item from cart | None |
| POST | `/clear` | Clear entire cart | None |

